msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: upstream/_posts/2016-06-30-devnation-live-blog-building-reactive.adoc:33
msgid "Posted by http://developers.redhat.com/blog/author/rctkv/[Rob Terzi] on June 29, 2016"
